{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 395.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I said, I went to visit my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he lowered his hand, but he never hit me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He says, go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "This time you can go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And so they respected-- big deal-- they respected the guys that spend a year, a year and a half in the camps already.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I mean that, hey, if you could survive all this time and still be alive, there's something to it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So he didn't hit me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And they would hit you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I mean, you could never forget this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Or sometimes, even kill you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So they respected the-- all the-- all the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And suddenly before [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] time, they also had, as a matter of fact, in there-- the camps had women, but not for the Jewish inmates.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They had a special barrack where they had women for the men, but only for the other nationalities, Polish or German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They were really mostly actually for the-- because there were quite a few German inmates also, prisoners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "So they would bring in and meet them there, the women for them, but not for the Jewish prisoners in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Just before the end, I-- I took sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And I was taken in to the hospital in Monowitz, in Buna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "There was a hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "The first time I was taken in was I lost feelings in my fingers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They were just numb, completely numb, and wouldn't come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And of course, if they would know about it, they would-- I would be taken immediately out of the workforce and into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There's someone who knew someone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "As I said, I've been in the camps for so long, that they took me in right after work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Again, it's experimental.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
